{"questionId":"9076848","questionHtml":"<p>Two strings of lengths <em>L</em><sub>1</sub> and <em>L</em><sub>2</sub> are fixed at both ends. The wavespeed is the same for&nbsp;both strings. They both vibrate at the same frequency. <em>L</em><sub>1</sub> vibrates at its first harmonic.&nbsp;<em>L</em><sub>2</sub> vibrates at its third harmonic.</p>\n<p>What is <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{{L_1}}}{{{L_2}}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>L</mi>\n          <mn>1</mn>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>L</mi>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>?</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>A.&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{1}{3}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mn>1</mn>\n    <mn>3</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>B.&nbsp; &nbsp;1</p>\n<p>C.&nbsp; &nbsp;2</p>\n<p>D.&nbsp; &nbsp;3</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>D</p>","meta":{"questionId":"9076848","referenceCode":"18N.1.SL.TZ0.17","subjectId":"46-dp-physics-last-assessment-2024","title":"Two strings of lengths L1 and L2 are fixed at both ends. The wavespeed is the same for both strings. They both vibrate at the same frequency. L1 vibrates at its first harmonic. L2 ","paper":"1","level":"SL","questionNumber":"17","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Core","Core","Topic 4: Waves","4.5 – Standing waves","Core","Topic 4: Waves"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}